    java.io.Serializable, TrainingWorker<ParameterAveragingTrainingResult>

    public class ParameterAveragingTrainingWorker
extends BaseTrainingWorker<ParameterAveragingTrainingResult>
    ParameterAveragingTrainingWorker implements standard parameter averaging every m iterations.
